Location is fantastic. It's a beachfront inn. Tbh we went there not knowing it's quite far from Gang-neung's famous beach and all the restaurants/cafe. We chose here solely because it was the one and only affordable beachfront option that allows our lovely doggo son(20lbs). The view was beyond amazing. We fell asleep with the sound of wave. The owner lady was so nice. They allowed us an early check-in. The dog fee was only KRW 5000. They also allowed us to have late dinner at the beach front porch. Super friendly place. Nice view.
